fields.name: Regular Seasonal Caravan pitch
fields.description: The majority of these pitches are 7 x 10 meter large grass pitches that are suitable for all units.Each pitch have electric  water & waste connections. One unit only per pitch. If you have 2 tents you must book 2 separate pitches.They come with electric hook up (min 10 amp).Please note that everything must fit on your pitch including ropes  awnings  pup tents  gazebos and your car.

fields.name: Tent pitch
fields.description: level pitches well laid out and spread over three different fields served by hard tarmac track. A small river flows along the eastern edge of the site with mature trees offering shelter. Overall the valley situation adds to the feeling of seclusion of this well-kept site.

fields.name: Tent pitch with power
fields.description: We have 22 level pitches well laid out and spread over three different fields served by hard tarmac track. A small river flows along the eastern edge of the site with mature trees offering shelter. Overall the valley situation adds to the feeling of seclusion of this well-kept site.

fields.name: Cabin bunkbed 4 people
fields.description: We are proud to present our beautiful Cabins which sleeps up to four guests. There is a small seating area with TV  fridge and kettle inside. Externally  there is a decked area with a table  chairs and chiminea for guests to use. is in a large  fenced enclosure which is vehicle free for your safety. There are also two camping pitches which are used at peak times.Guests staying in Millook have full use of the campsite toilets and showers  as well as the kitchen deck which is provided for our glamping guests. All bedding and one set of towels is provided  along with crockery and cutlery. Pans and cooking equipment are provided on the kitchen deck which also has gas burners  a freezer  wash up area and undercover dining area.
